WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.766 --> 00:00:01.800
What do I mean?

2
00:00:01.800 --> 00:00:03.666
Let me tell you clearly

3
00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:06.100
Li Xiaolin ran away

4
00:00:06.133 --> 00:00:08.266
Run into the mountains and forests

5
00:00:09.500 --> 00:00:12.666
I must have lost my way for a while and couldn't come back

6
00:00:12.666 --> 00:00:16.566
When he comes back, we will cook the raw rice into cooked rice.

7
00:00:17.700 --> 00:00:19.866
Hey, why are you here again?

8
00:00:20.600 --> 00:00:21.666
Let me tell you something.

9
00:00:21.666 --> 00:00:22.866
Go quickly

10
00:00:22.900 --> 00:00:26.000
If Li Xiaoling finds out, I can't report you

11
00:00:26.500 --> 00:00:27.600
Okay, okay.

12
00:00:27.766 --> 00:00:29.366
Pack up these things quickly

13
00:00:29.366 --> 00:00:30.700
I'm going to eat tonight

14
00:00:30.733 --> 00:00:33.866
Also, in the future, the heavy work of doing laundry and fetching water

15
00:00:33.866 --> 00:00:35.333
Don't let Li Mingyue do it

16
00:00:35.333 --> 00:00:37.466
You two can find a way to share it.

17
00:00:37.900 --> 00:00:40.533
Are you afraid that you were beaten silly by Li Xiaolin?

18
00:00:40.533 --> 00:00:42.100
Let me tell you something.

19
00:00:42.133 --> 00:00:44.766
I only recognize Li Xiaolin as a son-in-law now

20
00:00:45.266 --> 00:00:46.833
As for you?

21
00:00:46.933 --> 00:00:48.833
A month later.

22
00:00:49.333 --> 00:00:50.233
I'll transfer it to you.

23
00:00:50.866 --> 00:00:52.766
One month?

24
00:00:53.100 --> 00:00:55.233
I'm going to sit here tonight

25
00:00:55.400 --> 00:00:57.800
I will tell you Mingyue

26
00:00:57.800 --> 00:01:00.466
Li Xiaolin was maimed by our brothers

27
00:01:00.800 --> 00:01:02.866
Ran into the mountains and forests

28
00:01:02.900 --> 00:01:05.833
Li Mingyue can only marry me

29
00:01:06.566 --> 00:01:08.966
I don't want you for the money.

30
00:01:09.400 --> 00:01:11.566
Help take care of children in the future

31
00:01:11.700 --> 00:01:15.066
Don't make you two old godmothers less sick

32
00:01:15.133 --> 00:01:17.433
At that time, Li Mingyue felt sorry for him again

33
00:01:17.666 --> 00:01:19.466
I will also feel sorry.

34
00:01:19.866 --> 00:01:23.233
You just said that Li Xiaoling was beaten away by you

35
00:01:26.166 --> 00:01:28.966
How did you say it came before?

